Basic Instrutions:

On Cerebro in a terminal run:
>>roscore

in another terminal run:
>>enable_cerebro

ssh into wolverine (password is odroid):
>> wolverine

then while sshd into wolverine run:
>>enable_cerebro

Now run whatever package your heart desires...

More Advanced Instructions:

Some aliases have been set up on cerebro to make the commands simpler...
Here are the actual commands...

enable_cerebro = export ROS_MASTER_URI=http://cerebro:11311

wolverine = ssh odroid@wolverine


